725202f-a.title: Queens: 31st Street - 24th Avenue
725202f-a.text:
31st Street, west side, between 24th and Hoyt Avenues,
showing a group of two-story homes being demolished, where
a publio playground was later built. View 1 is south from
the former Dorothy Place toward Woyt Avenue; view 2 is
across the I.R.T. elevated from 24th Road, just east of 31st
Street; view 3 shows frame houses at the S.W. corner of 24th
Road.
P. L. Sperr  September 20, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
